org.jcvi.jillion.sam

Interface SamVisitor.SamVisitorCallback.SamVisitorMemento

  • Enclosing interface:
    SamVisitor.SamVisitorCallback

    public static interface SamVisitor.SamVisitorCallback.SamVisitorMemento
    SamVisitorMemento is a marker interface that SamParser instances can use to "rewind" back to the position in its SAM or BAM file in order to revisit portions of the that file. SamVisitor.SamVisitorCallback.SamVisitorMemento should only be used by the SamParser instance that generated it.
    Author:
    dkatzel
